Author information:
(1)Non-Communicable Diseases Research Center, Endocrinology and Metabolism 
Population Sciences Institute, Tehran University of Medical Sciences, No. 10, 
Al-e-Ahmad and Chamran Highway Intersection, Tehran 1411713137, Iran.
